Good afternoon, Raffaella.

It was good talking to you today.

To recap our conversation.

  1.  You will receive the contents settlement in three to five days
  2.  You will receive the stress benefit payment of $2,000 in the same tim=
e period.
  3.  You are to send us your vet fee and report for the cats being hurt fr=
om the claimed event.
  4.  I will update you on a monthly basis at the beginning of each month.
  5.  You would like your claim file from the date of loss to today to be s=
ent to you. I will get this actioned for you.
  6.  You will send me privacy requests for new information we have on file=
 including new claim notes from today onwards.

Kind regards,

Zach

