e it.</span><o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span><o:p><=
/o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Regarding updates, =
I am more then happy to update you on the first of each month, would you pr=
efer monthly contacts from me instead of fortnightly?</span><o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span><o:p><=
/o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Regarding further c=
laim files, we can send you assessor reports as we receive these from the a=
ssessor. It would be less prudent for us to resend you the entire claim fil=
e each month and not efficient for us
